{"tid":433903,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［賭博］第二日有人生大事參加，前一晚坐UO夜機...","createTime":"2017-10-12T19:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T17:39:15.000Z","uid":31920,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"43676c5c90d0fc1ca4fc45eab208edb92f1168f3","tid":433903,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:23:35.000Z","msg":"第二日朝早要返香港參加大部分大學生 一生人都係得一次既畢業禮，<br />\n前一晚坐UO返香港會唔會極度不智？<br />\n買左機票先好怕到時突然Delay或者又Cancel<br />\n一諗到到時就咁坐係架機度又無野做到急到瀨尿又想喊既感覺就好驚<br />\n窮學生去左外國進修<br />\n貪平同真係無多餘錢買傳統航空機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b5918af0e310280d5b877de39ae717696b433f","tid":433903,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:25:16.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"16b6648bba019f02d0cdaefbdb06979a80a02b59","tid":433903,"uid":7903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明知重要仲要搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9affbdd881001a370079c645ea1c7c589696a19f","tid":433903,"uid":36679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:27:20.000Z","msg":"呢d位真係唔好慳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2570f75ec47b9caa2ba3d9aad6980c18819a6f","tid":433903,"uid":15335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T21:51:20.000Z","msg":"訂早一日嘅廉航囉"},{"pid":"cd5b9b59bb7ee108c348635c41bcfe9cbf055e29","tid":433903,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T23:16:01.000Z","msg":"早幾日返"},{"pid":"c1e99ce11425c329944cabd995bef5bea2a1b759","tid":433903,"uid":99391,